Jeffry Wickham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeffry_Wickham 0 Jeffry Wickham (5 August 1933 – 17 June 2014) was an English film and television actor. He served as President of the actors' trade union Equity from 1992 to 1994 and was the father of the actress Saskia Wickham. His death after a long illness was announced on 18 June 2014.
